headline: Marsh McLennan’s CIO started with a summer job in 1995. He never left and now leads a team of more than 5,000 technologists
summary: CIO Paul Beswick leads a team of more than 5,000 technologists and says a key area of focus is ensuring all four of Marsh McLennan business divisions share ideas.
